{"tid":1615054,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"設立對本地商户企業單位民間制裁分級制度","createTime":"2019-10-03T03:28:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T12:07:11.000Z","uid":45486,"like":195,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":104,"replies":[{"pid":"fc94807f3d6636addde1449298a095ad9a0a18ba","tid":1615054,"uid":45486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:28:00.000Z","msg":"有見於大家對近兩日大量裝修post有意見，為避免各風向人士因而惡意利用，我覺得有必要設立分級制度，以釐清行動目標。<br />\n<br />\n分級制度共五級，根據該商户企業言論及行為而實施相應民間制裁：<br />\n<br />\n以下制裁程度由低至高<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第五級：杯葛，擺買，擺食</span><br />\n罪行：藍絲立場，藍絲言論。<br />\n例子：藍色商户<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">等四級：投訴（食環，稅局等)，不合作運動(齋坐，訂位，叫外賣等)；及包含第五級制裁。</span><br />\n罪行：所有實際行為支持撐警，如出席撐警集會，金錢，物資等商户企業<br />\n例子：空姐牛肉飯，華記正撚樣，大埔友口復等<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第三級：噴字，塗鴉，以重點及針對性、更直接影響及打擊其商業利為目標；及包含第四第五級制裁。</span><br />\n罪行：嚴重抹黑抗爭者<br />\n例子：TVB，美心集團等等<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第二級：武力制裁，破壞，裝修；及包含第三、四、五級制裁。</span><br />\n罪行：間接或直接令抗爭者及市民做成或將會做成實制傷亡；所有建制派辦事處。<br />\n例子：某某撞人的士及小巴，荃灣麻雀館等等<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第一級：全方位制裁</span><br />\n罪行：協助政府，警察打壓抗爭者<br />\n例子：港鐵，各建制議員辦事處<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟不才，暫時諗到咁多，我唔知我睇法岩唔岩，大家集思廣益一下。"},{"pid":"9849185ecbef61acdd777eba18f06ad439de4593","tid":1615054,"uid":79965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:36:00.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"e7f8440b3fc8522b79d95605224b1f161b27826d","tid":1615054,"uid":45486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:36:55.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"89aca88a1d556aac6cc942caad4b9bb1ef95543b","tid":1615054,"uid":42042,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:38:34.000Z","msg":"我覺得合理<br />\n<br />\n全方位破壞唔係唔得，但我認為未係時候，未可以一步到位。<br />\n所以集中港共紅底就夠。"},{"pid":"9c8e01f0e7ad2d5e8d5e28bc60d9b9cb732f9008","tid":1615054,"uid":20262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:39:34.000Z","msg":"正確"},{"pid":"ff6d72da5e1697540c70cb271f7d19b52bdbedc4","tid":1615054,"uid":38588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:40:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ec1625c9344ee33bec3b1b7a301483b49b79a36","tid":1615054,"uid":45486,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"89aca88a1d556aac6cc942caad4b9bb1ef95543b","tid":1615054,"uid":42042,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:38:34.000Z","msg":"我覺得合理<br />\n<br />\n全方位破壞唔係唔得，但我認為未係時候，未可以一步到位。<br />\n所以集中港共紅底就夠。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:40:34.000Z","msg":"無錯，目標要明確<br />\n未跟貼事情發展嘅人只會覺得我地係無差別破壞<br />\n文宣必須要做，等多啲人知"},{"pid":"024ea696c48e48ce599a7a8042aecfb8605adc3e","tid":1615054,"uid":27660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:42:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1616eecff5d3e9517be9df18c35befda5ee2233","tid":1615054,"uid":27660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:42:12.000Z","msg":"推撚爆"},{"pid":"aeda497d9452d0d7d4b372bfe484d02174d1ccd7","tid":1615054,"uid":27660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:42:25.000Z","msg":"爆撚推"},{"pid":"833684c3919cca9cab3a3408f878258a50fb30c2","tid":1615054,"uid":27660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:42:40.000Z","msg":"爆推撚"},{"pid":"24bd5f39fb7ec4286a53a4e081e97b74f508c597","tid":1615054,"uid":27660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:42:55.000Z","msg":"撚推爆"},{"pid":"03d34b734f2edb82d449c6ce0f4f5661a33caf93","tid":1615054,"uid":27660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:43:08.000Z","msg":"爆爆撚"},{"pid":"f272b0b8a4997aaaebe298d0d17b60b36a3766ba","tid":1615054,"uid":27660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:43:19.000Z","msg":"推撚推"},{"pid":"24af3b8345714c5a932f21ff922f0de8ec9651d3","tid":1615054,"uid":27660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:43:32.000Z","msg":"推推爆"},{"pid":"59b78cf3e29a212ff0795c3e3ed78d7